| D2: Department | [Department](file:///c:/Users/ELCOT/Documents/student%20result%20management%20system/app/models.py#30-34) | id, code, name |
| D3: Student | [Student](file:///c:/Users/ELCOT/Documents/student%20result%20management%20system/app/models.py#53-62) | id, user_id, roll_number, phone_number, year |
| D4: Mark | [Mark](file:///c:/Users/ELCOT/Documents/student%20result%20management%20system/app/models.py#64-81) | id, student_id, semester_id, subject_name, first_internal, second_internal, model_exam, university_exam |
| D5: Semester | [Semester](file:///c:/Users/ELCOT/Documents/student%20result%20management%20system/app/models.py#36-40) | id, number, label |
| D6: SubjectTemplate | [SubjectTemplate](file:///c:/Users/ELCOT/Documents/student%20result%20management%20system/app/models.py#42-51) | id, department_id, year, semester_id, subject_name |
